@startuml seq-revoke-cascade
!theme plain
title Sequence — Thu hồi Cascade (Patient revoke A → cascade B/C)

actor Patient
participant "PatientMobile" as PM
participant "Backend\n+ Relayer" as Backend
participant "ConsentLedger" as Contract
participant "Subgraph" as SG
database "KeyShare DB +\nConsent + DelegationLog" as DB
actor "Doctor B\n(delegated via A)" as DocB

== Phase A: Setup ban đầu ==

note over Patient, DB : 1. P grant A allowDelegate=true (Flow #6)\n2. A delegate B via grantUsingRecordDelegation\n   → recordDelegationSource[B's key] = A\n3. Backend log DelegationAccessLog(P, byA, newB)\n4. B claim KeyShare → có quyền đọc

== Phase B: Patient revoke A ==

Patient -> PM : Mở AccessLog → bấm Thu hồi A
PM -> Patient : Biometric MFA
PM -> PM : Sign RevokePermit (EIP-712)
PM -> Backend : POST /api/relayer/revoke-consent
Backend -> Contract : revokeBySig(P, A, cidHash)\n(sponsored)
Contract -> Contract : _consents[P,A,root].active = false
Contract -> Contract : emit ConsentRevoked

== Phase C: Backend cascade ==

SG -> Contract : poll events (30s)
SG -> Backend : handleConsentRevoked(P, A, root)

Backend -> DB : Walk chain → descendant cidHashes
Backend -> DB : Tầng 1: revoke KeyShare\nsender=A → status='revoked'
Backend -> DB : Tầng 2 (§13 fix): query\nDelegationAccessLog WHERE\nbyDelegatee=A → get [B, C, ...]
Backend -> DB : Cho mỗi recipient: revoke\nALL KeyShare rows (kể cả\nsender=P cascade share)
Backend -> DB : Update Consent table:\n(P,A,root) → revoked\n(P,B,root) → revoked\nNẾU B chỉ có delegation
note right of DB : Footgun #1: NẾU P đã\ndirect grant B sau A delegate,\nrecordDelegationSource[B]=0\n→ B's consent độc lập\n→ KHÔNG cascade revoke

Backend -> DocB : Socket.io push\n"consent:updated"

== Phase D: B kiểm tra access ==

DocB -> Backend : GET /api/key-share/record/:cidHash
Backend -> Contract : canAccess(P, B, cidHash)
Contract -> Contract : _hasValidNormalConsent:\nread recordDelegationSource[B]
alt B chỉ có delegation từ A
  Contract -> Contract : srcKey = (P, A, root)\nsrcConsent.active = false
  Contract --> Backend : false
  Backend --> DocB : 403 Forbidden
  note right of DocB : B mất quyền ✓ cascade
else B có direct grant từ P (Footgun #1 fix)
  Contract -> Contract : recordDelegationSource[B]\n= 0 → skip walk
  Contract -> Contract : Check B's own consent\n→ active
  Contract --> Backend : true
  Backend --> DocB : encryptedPayload
  note right of DocB : B GIỮ quyền — đúng ý P\n(P chỉ revoke A, không revoke B)
end

@enduml
